{"tid":2198170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫同好報名日本書法賽卻搞丟作品 男子自己寫還得獎","createTime":"2020-09-11T07:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T07:59:39.000Z","uid":34409,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4b9a57c05cfa32402c578ce1c0821dec8ad2123b","tid":2198170,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:10:04.000Z","msg":"〔記者王定傳／新北報導〕去年間，周姓男子受周姓女同好所託，幫忙報名參加「日本第71回全日學生書道展」，卻<span class=\"red\">不慎遺失同好作品，事後竟異想天開，自己拿毛筆書寫，還冒用周女名義落款，並將作品寄至日本參賽，結果作品竟然得獎，周女親赴日本領獎驚覺這根本不是她的作品，因此提告，新北地院審理後，依偽造私文書罪，判周男2個月徒刑。</span><br />\n<br />\n檢警調查，去年7月，周女因為想參加「日本第71回全日學生書道展」，得知有熱心的同好要幫忙報名，因此把作品寄給周男，委託他寄至日本參賽。<br />\n<br />\n怎料，周男卻不慎遺失周女的書法作品，事後竟異想天開，自己拿毛筆書寫，再冒用周女名義落款，把作品寄到日本參賽，後來還真的得獎。<br />\n<br />\n周女為此親赴日本領獎，驚覺展出的作品，根本不是她的筆跡，因此提告，周男坦承犯行，法官審理後依偽造私文書罪，判他2個月徒刑，可上訴。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3287919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287919&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fsg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=bb40b7c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3287919&h=035de52b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3287919</a>"},{"pid":"c8ab3804dd2d71371537d2b7f30da6c3ff2a55e0","tid":2198170,"uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:11:08.000Z","msg":"咁都得?"},{"pid":"a430c4b5d9e4ef6a664968123a8f03a0a863be33","tid":2198170,"uid":91771,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"幫女人做嘢=贏無得分，輸要死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4024aafa9fb9b28d4c4825b6e077f8494b442c90","tid":2198170,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202